      • onRFCardRemove

        public abstract int onRFCardRemove()
        Prompt to cardholder to remove contactless card, and power off the RF field. The call back function need doing as following steps: 1.call sdkSysBeepRfRemoveCard to play card operate complete sound. 2.call show led status of card operate complete. 3.call sdkPiccClose to power off RF field. 4.Display in LCD to cardholder to remove contactless card.
        Returns:
        EmvConstants.App_Confirm_OK EmvConstants.App_Confirm_Cancel EmvConstants.App_Confirm_Failure

      • onInputPwd

        public abstract PINResult onInputPwd​(int pinRetryCount,
                                     int pinMode,
                                     byte[] arith)
        EMV cvm verify,Prompt to cardholder to enter PIN.
        Parameters:
        pinRetryCount - If the pinMode is PINResult.PIN_MODE__OFFLINE_PLAIN PINResult.PIN_MODE__OFFLINE_ENCRYPT, this value is PIN retry times for offine PIN.
        pinMode - pin mode PINResult.PIN_MODE_ONLINE PINResult.PIN_MODE__OFFLINE_PLAIN PINResult.PIN_MODE__OFFLINE_ENCRYPT
        arith - when pinMode is PINResult.PIN_MODE__OFFLINE_ENCRYPT the pheCreditPwd store data for PIN_ISO_9564_2 arith.
        Returns:
        pinBlock PINResult

      • onWaitAppSelect

        public abstract int onWaitAppSelect​(java.util.List<AIDSelect> appList)
        EMV kernel provide the aid list for the cardholder to select If this call back function is not exist ,the kernel will use the default function to cardholder to select application. The language is to use English.
        Parameters:
        appList - the aid list.
        Returns:
        If the return value is greater than or equal to zero the value is The AID index selected；-1 EmvConstants.App_Confirm_Cancel -2 EmvConstants.App_Confirm_Failure

      • onCredentialVerify

        public abstract int onCredentialVerify()
        The unionpay PBOC cvm verify mode, credential verify 1. Get the TAG_CardHoldIdType and TAG_CardHoldIdNo tag value to display,and verify the credential information. 2. You can return value not 0 directly.
        Returns:
        EmvConstants.App_Confirm_OK EmvConstants.App_Confirm_Cancel EmvConstants.App_Confirm_Failure

      • onEmvProcessRefer

        public abstract int onEmvProcessRefer​(int referType)
        EMV refers processing flow when the issuer return refer response. 1. prompt card pan and "PLS CALL YOUR BANK" information. 2. When the bank accept the transaction , run setTLV(0x8A000000, "Y2".getBytes()); setTLV(0xDF811400, new byte[]{0x40}); 3. When the bank reject the transaction , run setTLV(0x8A000000, "Z2".getBytes()); setTLV(0xDF811400, new byte[]{0x00});
        Parameters:
        referType - REFER_TYPE_ICC REFER_TYPE_ISSUER
        Returns:
        EmvConstants.App_Confirm_OK EmvConstants.App_Confirm_Cancel EmvConstants.App_Confirm_Failure

      • onTornTransRecoverData

        public abstract int onTornTransRecoverData​(TornTransData transData)

        Parameters:
        transData - torn transaction
        Returns:
